# Services layer

- **LLM**: single async client (httpx) calling OpenAI-compatible chat completions; inject base URL, key, model, timeout from settings; log latency and errors with structlog.
- **Prompts**: system prompt encodes post template, char limit, and "no fabricated specs"; user content is raw listing text or normalized parser fields.
- **Publishing**: thin wrapper around `Bot` methods; no business logic duplicated from handlers beyond validation.
- **Stats**: read aggregates from DB (published, rejected, approve rate for auto mode); keep SQL or repository methods testable.
